  <description>Plants perennial, with globose tubers 10–200 mm diam.; periderm 0–0.5 mm. Stems 5–40
    cm. Leaves: basal leaves petiolate 6–20 cm, blade linear, 3–14 × 0.5–1.3 cm; cauline leaves
    sessile, blade linear, 1–10 cm, tapered to slender base. Inflorescences 1-bracteate, rarely with
    2 or more bracts; bracts reduced apically, scalelike. Flowers 5–12 mm diam.; sepals 5–7 mm;
    petals white to pinkish or rose (rarely yellow or orange) or white with pink-lavender
    candy-stripes, 7–14 mm; ovules 6. Seeds 2–3 mm diam., shiny and smooth; elaisome 1–2 mm. 2n =
    12–190.</description>
